name: forest-inventory-clearwater-county-minnesota
notes: The 1998 Forest Inventory data set is an ARC/INFO polygon coverage that encompasses the County Memorial Forest Land and Tax Forfeited Trust Lands of Clearwater County, Minnesota. The data set was developed by the Clearwater County Land and Forestry Department with assistance from private consultants: Pro-West and Associates, Walker, Minnesota; and the Land Management Information Center (LMIC), St. Paul, Minnesota. The data was interpreted from aerial photography (1:15,840 B&W IR) and field surveys of forest stands.
